/% =================[ Buildings

Fatieres convert PAG into Flesh over time; they require 1 cave and 10 metal to build.

Nests increase Leupai population over time, and decrease non-Leupai populations on occasion (chosen at random); they require 1 cave and at least three leupai to build.

Abittes allow the conversion of population units into Professors; they require 1 cave and 100 miracrystal to build.

Bovieteries increase PAG over time. Also, if the population includes any leupai, they increase Miratoxin over time as well. They require 50 metal, 30 crops, and 30 fattenium to build.

Processing Plants increase Processed Foods, PAG, Industrialization, and decrease Flesh and Crops over time, and allow the creation of Culinets; they require 100 metal, 50 crops, and 30 fattenium to build.

Laboratories allow the performance of Experiments on the population and planet, and randomly increase or decrease Planet Girth, Population, PAG, Animals, or Animal PAG over time. They may also change the planet Class, Atmosphere, Humidity, Water Type/Condition as well [random event]. Lastly, they allow the conversion of population units into Scientists. They require 1 cave, 200 metal, and 100 miracrystal to build.

Pump Plants allow direct fattening of the living planet, increasing Planet Girth and Flesh over time. They require 1 cave, 500 metal, 200 miracrystal, and 100 fattenium to build. %/

<<if ($leupaiPop gte 3) and ($planetCaves gte 1)>><<button [[+1 Nest (1 Cave)|passage()][$planetCaves -= 1; $planetNests += 1]]>><<endif>>

<<if ($planetMetal gte 10) and ($planetCaves gte 1)>><<button [[+1 Fatiere (10 Metal, 1 Cave)|passage()][$planetMetal += 10000; $planetCaves += 1; $planetFatieres += 1]]>><<endif>>

