/% =================[ Special Unlockables

Experimentation can have a variety of effects on the population and planet at random. It is unlocked as long as one Laboratory exists, and costs 10 Miracrystal to perform.

Treat Water allows your Scientists to spike the planet's water with various substances, and is unlocked once you've earned 50 research points.
	Clean Water costs 100 Metal, and changes the planet's water supply into [Any Non-Water]-->[Any Tainted Water]-->Clean Water.
	Slime Treatment costs 100 Slime, and changes the planet's water supply into Slime-Tainted Water-->Slime.
	Fertility Treatment costs 100 Miracrystal, and changes the planet's water supply into Fertile Water.
	Fattenium Treatment costs 100 Fattenium, and changes the planet's water supply into Fattenium Water-->Fattenium.
	Miratoxin Treatment costs 100 Miratoxin, and changes the planet's water supply into Somnus-->Miratoxin.
	Irradiate Water costs 100 Plutonium, and changes the planet's water supply into Dirty Water-->Toxic Sludge-->Plutonium. %/


