/% =================[ Farming & Hunting

As long as you have at least 1 basic population unit, they can be sent to hunt like a wildere, or gather crops like a culinet, but with decreased effectiveness.

Cavieres search for caves, increasing Caves over time, and occasionally increasing slime, metal, miracrystal, fattenium, plutonium, or aetherholes.

Wilderes hunt for meat and animal products, increasing Flesh [and appropriate resources] and decreasing Animals over time.

Culinets trap creatures, raise them for slaughter, and breed them for more Flesh yield, as well as butchering them on occasion-- increasing Population, PAG, Animals, Animal PAG, Crops, and Flesh over time, as well as occasionally decreasing Population and Animals at a much slower rate.

All processes that add Flesh yield more or less depending upon the PAG or Animal PAG of the planet. (todo) %/\
